{"tid":1520020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再提一次 唔好背向敵人","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:26:57.000Z","uid":225100,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0e4ca9bde5a07ff0ad28b70e3454823147f1fa","tid":1520020,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"打唔打前線決定<br />\n但無論點都總會有需要撤退嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n要安全撤退<br />\n想齊上齊落一個都不能少<br />\n前排手足就一定唔可以背向敵人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>邊後退邊用餐具指向敵人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n二三排手足<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要補位</strong></span> 唔好令防線打開缺口<br />\n可以的話後一排手足要捉實第一排手足嘅袋<br />\n確保唔會有手足被拉走同落單<br />\n然後後面手足要盡快撤離<br />\n預留足夠空位俾前線加速後退<br />\n後排亦要安排足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">哨兵確保逃生路線嘅安全</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有少量敵人係都要衝埋黎<br />\n以為我地咁就會驚會怯會亂會背向敵人<br />\n咁到時大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong><br />\n#ChiNazi<br />\n#831見<br />\n#901春袋<br />\n#902罷課"},{"pid":"2d0d841e7786e6055e3ec19f6a0f11e7bc7f9624","tid":1520020,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n林鄭你愈想我嬲我愈冷靜，吹咩？<br />\n等你set好晒場，仲走去踩咪好撚蝕，你當勇武on9咖？"},{"pid":"d5d884dbc20f5f8cacfcc5ef80e3205482be66a5","tid":1520020,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入黎幫推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k